Jagdish Bhagwati, professor of 
economics and law at Columbia University, discusses his new book
"Why Growth Matters: How Economic Growth in India Reduced 
Provery and the Lessons for Other Developing Countries." 
Bhagwati talks with Bloomberg's Kathleen Hays on Bloomberg 
Radio's "The Hays Advantage."    (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 17:51
 